#: includes/class-ddp-admin.php:178
msgid "Usage and FAQ"
msgstr "Brug og ofte stillede spørgsmål"

#: includes/class-ddp-admin.php:180
msgid "What does this plugin do?"
msgstr "Hvad gør dette plugin?"

#: includes/class-ddp-admin.php:181
msgid ""
"Helps you clean duplicate posts from your blog. The plugin checks for "
"blogposts on your blog with the same title."
msgstr ""
"Hjælper dig med at fjerne duplikatindlæg fra din blog. Plugin'et tjekker for "
"blogindlæg på din blog med samme titel."

#: includes/class-ddp-admin.php:182
msgid ""
"It can run automatically via WordPress's own internal CRON-system, or you "
"can run it automatically."
msgstr ""
"Det kan køre automatisk via WordPress' eget interne CRON-system, eller du "
"kan køre det automatisk."

#: includes/class-ddp-admin.php:183
msgid ""
"It also has a nice feature that can send you an e-mail when Delete Duplicate "
"Posts finds and deletes something (if you have turned on the CRON feature)."
msgstr ""
"Den har også en fin funktion, der kan sende dig en e-mail, når Delete "
"Duplicate Posts finder og sletter noget (hvis du har slået CRON-funktionen "
"til)."

#: includes/class-ddp-admin.php:184
msgid "Help! Something was deleted that was not supposed to be deleted!"
msgstr "Hjælp mig! Noget blev slettet, som ikke skulle slettes!"

#: includes/class-ddp-admin.php:185
msgid ""
"I am sorry for that, I can only recommend you restore the database you took "
"just before you ran this plugin."
msgstr ""
"Det er jeg ked af. Jeg kan kun anbefale, at du gendanner den database, du "
"tog, lige før du kørte dette plugin."

#: includes/class-ddp-admin.php:186
msgid ""
"If you run this plugin, manually or automatically, it is at your OWN risk!"
msgstr ""
"Hvis du kører dette plugin, manuelt eller automatisk, er det på din EGEN "
"risiko!"

#: includes/class-ddp-admin.php:187
msgid ""
"We have done our best to avoid deleting something that should not be "
"deleted, but if it happens, there is nothing we can do to help you."
msgstr ""
"Vi har gjort vores bedste for at undgå at slette noget, der ikke bør "
"slettes, men hvis det alligevel sker, kan vi desværre ikke hjælpe dig."

#. translators: %d: Number of duplicates deleted.
#: includes/class-ddp-admin.php:216
#, php-format
msgid "Deleted %d duplicate posts."
msgstr "Slettet %d dubletter."

