#. translators: %s: Total number of deleted duplicates
#: includes/class-ddp-admin.php:449
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Hey, I noticed this plugin has deleted %s duplicate posts for you - that's "
"awesome! Could you please do me a BIG favor and give it a 5-star rating on "
"WordPress? Just to help us spread the word and boost our motivation."
msgstr ""
"Hej, jeg bemærkede, at dette plugin har slettet %s duplikerede indlæg for "
"dig - det er fantastisk! Vil du gøre mig en STOR tjeneste og give det en 5-"
"stjernet vurdering på WordPress? Bare for at hjælpe os med at sprede ordet "
"og øge vores motivation."

#: includes/class-ddp-admin.php:453
msgid "Ok, you deserve it"
msgstr "Okay, du fortjener det"

#: includes/class-ddp-admin.php:464
msgid ""
"Sign up to our newsletter to receive the latest tips and updates directly to "
"your inbox. Ensure your WordPress site remains efficient and duplicate-free!"
msgstr ""
"Tilmeld dig vores nyhedsbrev for at modtage de nyeste tips og opdateringer "
"direkte i din indbakke. Sørg for, at din WordPress-hjemmeside forbliver "
"effektiv og fri for dubletter!"

