msgstr "Slet dublerede indlæg Pro"

#: includes/class-ddp-admin.php:507
msgid ""
"Pro adds deeper cleanup controls for sites that need more than a basic title "
"scan."
msgstr ""
"Pro-versionen indeholder mere avancerede rydningsfunktioner til websteder, "
"der kræver mere end en simpel titelscanning."

