msgstr "(%s i alt fundet)"

#: includes/class-ddp-admin.php:658
msgid "Choose which post types to scan for duplicates."
msgstr "Vælg, hvilke indlægstyper der skal scannes for dubletter."

#: includes/class-ddp-admin.php:664
msgid "Post status"
msgstr "Status for indlæg"

#: includes/class-ddp-admin.php:703
msgid ""
"Warning: Enabling this can give false results. Only enable if you know what "
"you are doing."
msgstr ""
"Advarsel: Aktivering af dette kan give falske resultater. Aktivér den kun, "
"hvis du ved, hvad du laver."

#: includes/class-ddp-admin.php:720
msgid ""
"Free version scans published posts only. Pro can include drafts, scheduled, "
"private, and other statuses."
msgstr ""
"Gratisversionen scanner kun offentliggjorte indlæg. Pro-versionen kan også "
"omfatte kladder, planlagte indlæg, private indlæg og indlæg med andre "
"statuser."

